# Title: Potential MsiExec Masquerading
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2019-11-14
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the execution of msiexec.exe from an uncommon directory
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1036.005
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_msiexec_masquerading.yml

Image="*\\msiexec.exe" OR OriginalFileName="\\msiexec.exe" NOT (Image IN ("C:\\Windows\\System32\\*", "C:\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\*", "C:\\Windows\\WinSxS\\*"))